        startVolumeID - (optional) The ID of the first volume to list.
        limit - (optional) The maximum number of volumes to return from the API.
        volumeStatus - (optional) If specified, filter to only volumes with the provided status.

      • getIsPaired

        public Optional<Boolean> getIsPaired()
